| Plot                    = [[File:Guardians of the Galaxy - Cosmic Rewind Title 001.png|right|thumb|300px]]
[[File:Guardians of the Galaxy - Cosmic Rewind - Energy Pavillon Symbol 001.jpg|right|thumb|200px|The new logo of the Energy Pavilion, reminiscent of the [[Nova Corps]] symbol]]
The adventure starts in the “Galaxarium,” a planetarium-like exhibition that explores the similarities and mysteries of the formation of Earth’s galaxy and [[Xandar]]. You’ll be invited to learn more about Xandar’s treasures – until the moment when the Guardians of the Galaxy arrive, and adventures across the cosmos ensue.<ref name="first">{{cite web|url=
https://disneyparks.disney.go.com/blog/2019/09/take-a-first-look-at-the-guardians-of-the-galaxy-cosmic-rewind-ride-vehicles/|title=Take a First Look at the Guardians of the Galaxy: Cosmic Rewind Ride Vehicles|work=Disney Parks Blog|first=Thomas|last=Smith|date=25 August 2019|accessdate=15 Feb 2021}}</ref>
